ARTICLE.TITLE: Police searching for missing 11-year-old boy last seen in east Columbus
ARTICLE.TEXT:
Anyone with information is asked to call Columbus police at 614-645-4624.

UPDATE: Javeiontay Wallace was found in Whitehall and returned home safely.

COLUMBUS, Ohio— Columbus police are asking for help searching for a missing child in east Columbus.

Eleven-year-old Javeiontay Wallace was last seen on Monday in the area of Atcheson Avenue and Trevitt Street.

Wallace is a black male, 4’8” and weighs about 90 pounds. He has black hair and brown eyes

He was last seen wearing a blue, short-sleeved shirt and tan pants.
